front.title: •Sith Fury (V)
front.gametext: USED: If you just drew a character for destiny, take that card into hand to cancel and redraw that destiny.  LOST: Once per game, exchange a Dark Jedi in hand with a Dark Jedi in Lost Pile.
front.lore: At his peak, no one could stand up to the Dark Lord of the Sith. His superior tactics devastated those who opposed him.
